@startuml Food Logging Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - Food Logging Flow

actor User
participant "HomeScreen\n(Dashboard)" as Home
participant "FoodSearchScreen" as Search
participant "FoodCacheService" as Cache
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase
participant "FoodDatabase\n(Local)" as LocalDB
participant "MealSelectionDialog" as Dialog
participant "AppProvider" as Provider

== Open Food Search ==

User -> Home: Click "+ Add Food" button\nfor meal type (Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner/Snack)
activate Home

Home -> Search: Navigate with mealType parameter
activate Search

Search -> Search: Initialize search
Search -> Cache: checkCacheValidity()
activate Cache

alt Cache Invalid or Empty
    Cache -> Supabase: getAllFoods()
    activate Supabase
    Supabase --> Cache: List<Food>
    deactivate Supabase
    Cache -> Cache: Save to local cache\nwith timestamp
    Cache --> Search: Foods loaded
else Cache Valid
    Cache --> Search: Return cached foods
end
deactivate Cache

Search -> LocalDB: Load local food database
activate LocalDB
LocalDB --> Search: Additional local foods
deactivate LocalDB

Search --> User: Show food search interface\n(Search bar + Food grid)

== Search for Food ==

User -> Search: Type food name in search bar
Search -> Search: Filter foods by query\n(case-insensitive)
Search --> User: Show matching foods\n(with emoji, name, calories)

User -> Search: Select a food from results
Search --> User: Show food details card:\n- Name & Emoji\n- Serving size\n- Calories\n- Protein, Carbs, Fat

== Select Meal Type & Servings ==

Search -> Dialog: Show MealSelectionDialog
activate Dialog

Dialog --> User: Show:\n- Meal type selector\n- Servings adjuster (0.5-10)\n- Nutritional preview
User -> Dialog: Adjust servings (e.g., 1.5)
Dialog -> Dialog: Update nutrition preview:\n  calories * servings\n  protein * servings\n  carbs * servings\n  fat * servings

User -> Dialog: Confirm meal type
User -> Dialog: Click "Add to Log"

Dialog -> Provider: addMeal(food, mealType, servings)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Create MealLog:\n- Generate unique ID\n- Store food data\n- Store meal type\n- Store servings\n- Timestamp with selected date

Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences\n(persist locally)
Provider -> Provider: Update consumed totals
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Dialog: Meal logged
deactivate Provider

alt Sync to Supabase Enabled
    Dialog -> Supabase: logMeal({\n  mealType, foodName,\n  calories, protein,\n  carbs, fat, servings, date\n})
    activate Supabase
    Supabase --> Dialog: Synced to cloud
    deactivate Supabase
end

Dialog --> User: Show success message
Dialog -> Search: Close dialog
deactivate Dialog

Search -> Home: Navigate back
deactivate Search

== Update Dashboard ==

Home -> Provider: Listen to state changes
activate Provider
Provider --> Home: Updated data:\n- consumedCalories\n- consumedProtein\n- consumedCarbs\n- consumedFat
deactivate Provider

Home --> User: Refresh dashboard:\n- Update calorie ring\n- Update macro bars\n- Update meal cards\n- Show new meal entry

deactivate Home

== Remove Meal ==

User -> Home: Swipe to delete meal\nor click remove icon
activate Home

Home -> Provider: removeMeal(mealId)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Remove from meal logs
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: Recalculate totals
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Home: Meal removed
deactivate Provider

alt Sync Enabled
    Home -> Supabase: deleteMealLog(mealId)
    activate Supabase
    Supabase --> Home: Deleted from cloud
    deactivate Supabase
end

Home --> User: Update UI\n(meal removed)
deactivate Home

note right of Provider
  **Calorie Tracking:**
  - Target: 2000 kcal
  - Consumed: 1650 kcal
  - Remaining: 350 kcal
  - Progress: 82.5%

  **Macros:**
  Protein: 120g / 150g (80%)
  Carbs: 180g / 200g (90%)
  Fat: 50g / 67g (75%)
end note

@enduml

